dct_title_s: Relief map of New Jersey : based upon the Topographical Survey
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading. Relief map is accompanied by "Name sheet" with note : "Localities may be identified on the Relief Map by laying this sheet over it in proper position." At head of title: Geological survey of New Jersey. Historic Maps copy imperfect: "Name sheet" wanting.
